<LegalLayout title="Privacy Policy | Slimkay" description="How Slimkay collects and handles website enquiries, analytics data, and direct contact details.">
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="updated">Last updated: 8 May 2026</p>

  <p>This policy explains how Slimkay handles personal information collected through slimkay.co.za and www.slimkay.co.za.</p>

  <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>When you send a booking enquiry, we may collect your name, email address, phone number, event details, venue or city, set length, and any message you choose to provide. We also receive basic website analytics through Umami.</p>

  <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
  <p>We use enquiry details to respond to bookings, discuss event requirements, keep a record of conversations, and improve the website experience. Website contact form submissions are sent to the Brightsync contact submissions API.</p>

  <h2>Third-Party Providers</h2>
  <p>The site uses Brightsync services for contact form handling, Umami for privacy-focused analytics, and static hosting infrastructure for delivery. We do not sell personal information.</p>

  <h2>Retention</h2>
  <p>Booking enquiries may be kept for as long as needed to respond, manage event planning, and maintain reasonable business records.</p>

  <h2>Your Rights</h2>
  <p>You can request access, correction, or deletion of your personal information by contacting Slimkay directly.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>Email <a href="mailto:bookings.slimkay@gmail.com">bookings.slimkay@gmail.com</a> or call <a href="tel:+27659650669">065 965 0669</a>.</p>
</LegalLayout>
